134
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,079
Have you decided what to paint?

135
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:51,079
Tell me,

136
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:52,959
Zhou Wan,

137
00:07:54,959 --> 00:07:56,240
